title: A Silver Kayle Main Looking for Jungler or Mid main to climb with
body: I'm a Top Kayle main looking for a duo to help climb out of silver and into gold for the first time. I have been in silver for I think 3 seasons now and want to make my game better and climb to that Gold Heaven haha.
